PHP Code: $layout_name
<?PHP echo $layout_name; ?> - Layout root path 
Example
http://example.com/layouts/layout/
Example 2
 
<img src="<?PHP echo $layout_name; ?>/images/logo.jpg" alt="Logo" /> --> Load logo from layouts/name/images/

PHP Code: $title
<?PHP echo $title ?> - Page Title Head
Example
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="content-language" content="pl">
<title><?PHP echo $title ?></title>
</head>
<body>
</body>
</html>

PHP Code: $main_content
<?PHP echo $main_content; ?> - Show content
Example
<div class="content">
<?PHP echo $main_content; ?>
</div>

PHP Code: $topic
<?PHP echo $topic; ?> - Show Topic Name
Example
<div class="subpage_title">
<?PHP echo $topic; ?>
</div>

Example layout.php

<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="content-language" content="en">
<meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta http-equiv="Reply-to" content="webmaster@example.com" />
<meta name="Keywords" content="Keywords...." />
<meta name="Description" content="Description..." />
<meta name="Author" content="Author...." />
<title><?PHP echo $title ?></title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="<?PHP echo $layout_name; ?>/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
<img src="<?PHP echo $layout_name; ?>/images/logo.jpg" alt="Logo" />

<div class="subpage_title">
<?PHP echo $topic; ?>
</div>

<div class="content">
<?PHP echo $main_content; ?>
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>

Example config_layout.ini

darkborder = "#9E7B5D"
lightborder = "#B09165"
vdarkborder = "#845B3B"
news_title_color = "white"
logo_monster = "Frost Dragon"

